				  <br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			        &nbsp; F monster practice -   
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Go to practice mode, highlight the monster above a monster that has not been captured yet, then press Circle + Down</font>&nbsp;
			        <br>&nbsp; Grow or Shrink -   
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">At the character selection screen hold L2 + R2 and press X to choose your character. During the game press L2 to shrink and R2 to grow</font>&nbsp;
			        <br>&nbsp; Repeat Victory Speech -   
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">As soon as your character finishes their victory speech press L2 + Left</font>&nbsp;
			        <br>&nbsp; Victory Dance -   
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Win both rounds of a match, then hold Up + Right + L2</font>&nbsp;<br>
				  <br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">ACTION REPLAY CODES:</font></i></u><br>
